OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools keep pupils indoors
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter email threat         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A number of schools in Leeds and       
OL,6, Bradford kept pupils inside on Thursday
OL,7, after receiving an email threat.       
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire Police said it had      
OL,10,Flaunched an investigation and was      
OL,11,Fproviding "reassurance and safety      
OL,12,Fadvice to affected schools".           
OL,14,FAccording to messages sent from schools
OL,15,Fto parents, officers were treating the 
OL,16,Fthreat as "credible".                  
OL,18,FLeeds City Council said it was "aware  
OL,19,Fof an ongoing situation" and working   
OL,20,Fwith police to support schools.        
